short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension expedites the process of entering Infusionsoft contact data into CSG Actuarial and Whitepages.com forms.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
